<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. لِيُهْدَى بِكَ الْمَرْءُ الَّذِي بِكَ يَقْتَدِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حَرِيصًا عَلَى نَفْعِ الْوَرَى وَهُدَاهُمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تَنَلْ كُلَّ خَيْرٍ فِي نَعِيمٍ مُؤَبَّدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكُنْ صَابِرًا بِالْفَقْرِ وَادَّرِعِ الرِّضَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بِمَا قَدَّرَ الرَّحْمَنُ وَاشْكُرْهُ تُحْمَدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَمَا الْعِزَّ إِلا فِي الْقَنَاعَةِ وَالرِّضَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِأَدْنَى كِفَافٍ حَاصِلٍ وَالتَّزَهُّدِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَمَنْ لَمْ يُقْنِّعْهُ الْكَفَافُ فَمَا إِلَى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>رِضَاهُ سَبِيلٌ فَاقْتَنِعْ وَتَقَصَّدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَمَنْ يَتَغَنَّى يُغْنِهِ اللهُ وَالْغِنَى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>غِنَى النَّفْسُ لا عَنْ كَثْرَةِ الْمُتَعَدِّدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَإِيَّاكَ وَالإِعْجَابَ وَالْكِبْرَ تُحْظَ بِالسَّـ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عَادَةِ فِي الدَّارَيْنِ فَارْشُدْ وَأَرْشِدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَهَا قَدْ بَذَلْتُ النُّصْحَ جُهْدِي وَإِنَّنِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مُقِرٌّ بِتَقْصِيرِي وَبِاللهِ أَهْتَدِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَقَضَّتْ بِحَمْدِ اللهِ لَيْسَتْ ذَمِيمَةً<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلَكِنَّهَا كَالدُّرِّ فِي عِقْدِ خُرَّدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>يَحَارُ لَهُ قَلْبُ اللَّبِيبُ وَعَارِف<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>كَرِيمَانِ إِنْ جَالا بِفِكْرٍ مُنَضَّدِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَمَا رَوْضَةٌ خُفَتْ بِنُورِ رَبِيعِهَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>بِسَلْسَالِهَا الْعَذْبُ الزُّلالِ الْمُبَرَّدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>